{"tid":1281241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何檢舉翻牆的中國網民？這招幫助他們找到回家的路","createTime":"2019-07-03T08:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T06:32:57.000Z","uid":130724,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7dfcf1161314c36fc4f2ac4e362a2cc7c18fb18","tid":1281241,"uid":130724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zi.media/@hugo3c/post/wUUnmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzi.media%2F%40hugo3c%2Fpost%2FwUUnmQ&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=172a61f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zi.media/@hugo3c/post/wUUnmQ</a><br />\n<br />\n常常在臉書、YouTube 上看到各種從大陸翻牆過來的網友，發表各種侵略性的言論嗎？現在有方法可以「回敬」他們了，而且是 100% 合法的方式，利用中國的中央網信辦 (國家互聯網信息辦公室)，檢舉違法利用 VPN 等翻牆軟體過來的民眾，將留言截圖 (越多越好)，就可以請這些網民「回家」吃自己啦！<br />\n<br />\n國家互聯網信息辦公室：<a href=\"http://www.12377.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.12377.cn%2F&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=b39c116e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.12377.cn/</a><br />\n檢舉中國翻牆網友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n△ 點擊上方連結進入中央網信辦，點擊「違法和不良信息舉報入口」<br />\n<br />\n中央網信辦<br />\n△ 接著會有個舉報須知，大概看一下就好 XD 不過看完滑到最下面有個同意需要按一下才能繼續下一步。<br />\n<br />\n中央網信辦"},{"pid":"07bc87586b4c7571bbd24ff610dee4519edd8baf","tid":1281241,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad7afd2e66990d601767da9af545bc966b9ba519","tid":1281241,"uid":35633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n行得正企得正唔使怕喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88f8c173d03d8dfd3be71e8b9813ca278e520b7","tid":1281241,"uid":24127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f18bb03c8a47a4db581b7204910014793f61164c","tid":1281241,"uid":24127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:49:26.00